  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC073">
          <l>mūṉṟā kuvatē,</l>
	<l>oṭuveṉap peyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi</l>
	<l>viṉaimutal karuvi yaṉaimutaṟ ṟatuvē.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/56/mode/1up">56</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/57/mode/1up">57</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ic cūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, muṟaiyāṉē mūṉṟām vēṟṟumai yuṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
urai: mūṉṟām eṇṇu muṟaimaikkaṇṇatu oṭu eṉṉum peyaraiyuṭaiya vēṟṟumaic col; atu viṉai mutalum karuviyum eṉa iraṇṭiṉaiyum taṉakkup poruḷāka uṭaiyatu eṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu: 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘nāyāṟ kōṭpaṭṭāṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu viṉai mutalpaṟṟi vantatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘vēlāl eṟintāṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu karuvipaṟṟi vantatu.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi, avviṉaimutalum karuviyum paṟṟi varumāṟṟai virikkiṉṟār:
      </p>
      <p>
ataṉiṉiyaṟal,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit3">
        <l>‘taccaṉ ceyta ciṟumā vaiyam’</l>
        <trailer>[kuṟuntokai — 61.]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
itu taccaṉāṟ ceyyappaṭṭatu eṉpatām.
      </p>
      <p>
ataṟṟaku kiḷavi:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit4">
       <l>‘vāyāṟṟakkatu vāycci’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
ataṉ viṉaippaṭutal:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit5">
       <l>‘nāyāṟ kōṭpaṭṭāṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
ataṉiṉātal:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit6">
       <l>‘vāṇikattāṉāyiṉāṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
ataṉiṟ kōṭal:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit7">
       <l>‘kāṇattāṟ koṇṭa arici’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
ataṉoṭu mayaṅkal:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit8">
       <l>‘eḷḷoṭu virāaya arici’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
ataṉōṭu iyainta oruviṉaik kiḷavi:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit9">
        <l>‘cāttaṉoṭu vantāṉ koṟṟaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
ataṉoṭiyainta vēṟuviṉaik kiḷavi:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit10">
        <l>‘muttoṭu muḻāk kōttu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
        ovvātataṉai oppittal oppaloppurai.
      </p>
      <p>
        iṉṉāṉ eṉpuḻiyum ētu viṉkaṇṇum varum mūṉṟām vēṟṟumai. iṉṉāṉ eṉpatu,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit11">
        <l>‘kaṇṇāṟ kottai, kālāṉ muṭavaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpaṉa.
      </p>
      <p>
ētu eṉpatu,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Ilam-cit12">
        <l>‘muyaṟciyāṟ piṟattalāṉ collu nilaiyātu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
aṉṉa piṟavum eṉṟataṉāl, piṟavum varuvaṉa ellām koḷka. (11)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n77/mode/1up">74</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n78/mode/1up">75</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. mēl oṭuveṉap peyar koṭuttōtiya vēṟṟumaiccol mūṉṟāvatām. atu viṉaimutaluṅ karuviyumākiya iraṇṭumutalaiyum poruḷākavuṭaittu e-ṟu.</p>
<p>mēl aiyoṭu kuvveṉṟōtiyavaḻi āṉurupuntaḻuvappaṭṭamaiyāṉ, īṇṭum avvāṟē koḷḷappaṭum; paṭavē, mūṉṟāvatātalum viṉaimutal karuvipporuṭṭātalum āṉurupiṟkumeytum.</p>
<p>viṉaimutalāvatu karuvi mutalāyiṉa kāraṇaṅkaḷait toḻiṟpaṭuttuvatu. karuviyāvatu viṉaimutaṟṟoḻiṟpayaṉaic ceyappaṭuporuṭkaṇuyppatu.</p>
<p>aṉaiyeṉpatu attaṉmaiyavākiya mutaleṉa avaṟṟatilakkaṇattiṟkut tōṟṟuvāy ceytavāṟu.</p>
<p>mutaleṉpataṟku mēlēyuraittām.</p>
<p>u - m. koṭiyoṭu tuvakkuṇṭāṉ; ūciyoṭu kuyiṉṟa tūcum paṭṭum. e - m. akattiyaṉāṟṟamiḻuraikkappaṭṭatu; vēlāṉeṟintāṉ. e-m. varum.</p>
<p>piṟaporuḷumuḷavēṉum viṉaimutal karuvi ciṟantamaiyāṉ, viṉaimutalkaruviyaṉaimutaṟṟeṉṟār.</p>
<p>viṉaimutalkaruvikkaṇ oṭuveṉurupu ikkālattarukiyallatu vārātu.	(12)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/n116/mode/1up">88</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/n118/mode/1up">90</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, muṟaiyāṉē mūṉṟāva tipporuṭkaṇ varumeṉkiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) oṭuveṉap peyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi mūṉṟākuvatē ― mēloṭuveṉap peyarkoṭuttōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaic coṉ mūṉṟāvatām, atu viṉaimutal karuvi aṉaimutaṟṟu ― atu viṉaimutaluṅ karuviyumākiya vavviraṇṭu kāraṇattaiyum poruḷāka vuṭait teṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
mēlataṉi ṉiyaṟaṉ mutaliyaṉa vāṉurupiṟ kēṟpa vuṭampoṭu puṇarttuc cūttirañ ceytali ṉavaṟṟiṟku muṟkoṇṭa vōṭeṉpataṟkum āl eṉpataṟkum viṉai mutal karuvi koḷka. āṉālāyt tirintum niṟkum.
      </p>
      <p>
‘viṉaimutal karuttā’ veṉpaṉa voṉṟu. karuttā niṉṟu taṉṉai yoḻinta karuvimutaliya kāraṇaṅkaḷēḻaṉai yuṅkāriyattiṉ kaṇikaḻttutali, ṉataṉai viṉaimutaleṉṟār.
      </p>
      <p>
iḵtu, iyaṟṟum viṉaimutalu mēvum viṉaimutalumeṉa viruvakaippaṭum. ‘koṭiyoṭu tuvakkuṇṭā’ ṉeṉpatiyaṟṟum viṉaimutal. atu, koṭitaṉṉōṭu tuvakku talaic ceyyappaṭṭāṉ cāttaṉeṉṉum poruṭṭu. koṭiyiṉatu nikaḻcci, yīṇṭuk karuvi. koṭi cāttaṉait toḻiluṟu vikkuṅ kāṟṟā ṉavaṉai nīṅkā vuṭaṉikaḻcciyai viḷakkiṟṟu oṭu veṉṉurupu. aracaṉā liyaṟṟappaṭṭa tēvakulam’ eṉpatēvum viṉaimutal.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi, ‘karuvi’ kāraṇa, mētu, nimitta’, meṉpaṉa, tammuḷ vēṟupā ṭuṭaiya vēṉu motta <note place="foot">poruḷaṉa (pā. pō.)</note>poruṭṭu. akkāraṇam. mutaṟkāraṇamun tuṇaikkāraṇamumeṉa viruvakaippaṭum. mutaṟ kāraṇamāvatu kāriyattōṭoṟṟumaiyuṭaiyatu, tuṇaik kāraṇamāvatu, ammutaṟ kāraṇattiṟkut tuṇaiyākya viṉaimutaliya veṭṭum. akkaruviyāvatu, viṉaimutaṟṟoḻiṟpayaṉaic ceyappaṭu poruṭkaṇuyppatu. atuvumiyaṟṟutaṟ karuviyākiya kārakak karuviyum, aṟitaṟ karuviyākiya ñāpakak karuviyu meṉa viruvakaippaṭum. ūciyoṭu kuyiṉṟa tūcum paṭṭum’ eṉpatu kārakak karuvi. atu, ūci koṇṭu cāttaṉ kuyilu talaic ceyyappaṭṭa tūcum paṭṭu meṉṉum poruṭṭu. cāttaṉ ṟoḻiṟpayaṉai yūci tūcilum paṭṭilum nikaḻttiṟṟu. itu tuṇaikkāraṇam. maṇṇāṉiyaṉṟa kuṭam — mutaṟkāraṇam. ituvuṅkārakakkaruvi. uṇarviṉāṉuṇarntāṉ: pukaiyiṉā leriyuḷḷa tuṇarntāṉ ― ivai ñāpakak karuvi. ivaṟṟiṟ kuṇarvu mutaṟ kāraṇam. kārakamāvatu toḻilai yiyaṟṟuvippatu. ñāpakamāvataṟivippatu.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi, āl akattiyaṉāṟ ṟamiḻuraikkap paṭṭatu; vēlā leṟintāṉ eṉavum. ōṭu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘ulakattō ṭoṭṭa voḻukal’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘kāvō ṭaṟakkuḷam toṭṭāṉum’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Nacc-cit3">
        <l>‘nāvīṟ ṟirunta pulamā makaḷōṭu naṉpoṟ</l>
        <l>pūvīṟ ṟirunta tirumā makaḷ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavum varum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC073-Nacc-cit4">
        <l>‘itunaṉipayakku mitaṉā ṉeṉṉum’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
iḵtu, āṉ vantatu eṉa varum. <num xml:lang="en">(12)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
